@startuml SyncSuccessFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Sincronização Pull - Sucesso (RF004, RF005 - UC001)
participant UI
participant SyncEngine
participant Plugin
participant DataSource
participant RxDB

UI -> SyncEngine: triggerSync()
SyncEngine -> Plugin: getLastCheckpoint()
Plugin -> SyncEngine: retorna checkpoint (updatedAt)

SyncEngine -> Plugin: pull(checkpoint)
Plugin -> DataSource: GET /issues?updated>checkpoint
DataSource -> Plugin: JSON (tarefas + metadata)

Plugin -> Plugin: Mapeia para padrão interno (RF005)
Plugin -> SyncEngine: tasks[], metadata[], timeEntries[]

SyncEngine -> RxDB: upsert tasks
SyncEngine -> RxDB: upsert timeEntries
SyncEngine -> RxDB: upsert metadata
RxDB -> SyncEngine: OK

SyncEngine -> Plugin: saveCheckpoint(newUpdatedAt)
SyncEngine -> UI: syncComplete(success)
UI -> UI: Atualiza indicador de sync
@enduml
